quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  2,1,Alif-Lãm-Mĩm
  2,2,This is the Book! There is no doubt about it—a guide for those mindful ˹of God˺
  2,3,"who believe in the unseen, establish prayer, and donate from what We have provided for them"
  2,4,"and who believe in what has been revealed to you ˹O Prophet˺ and what was revealed before you, and have sure faith in the Hereafter"
  2,5,"It is they who are ˹truly˺ guided by their Lord, and it is they who will be successful"
  2,6,"As for those who persist in disbelief, it is the same whether you warn them or not—they will never believe"
  2,7,"God has sealed their hearts and their hearing, and their sight is covered. They will suffer a tremendous punishment"